name: LUTROPIN ALFA
breadcrumbs: 6.5 Hypothalamic and pituitary hormones and anti-oestrogens
6.5.1 Hypothalamic and anterior pituitary hormones and anti-oestrogens
side-effects:
Side-effects nausea, vomiting, abdominal and pelvic pain; headache,
somnolence; injection-site reactions; ovarian hyperstimulation syndrome,
ovarian cyst, breast pain, ectopic pregnancy; thromboembolism, adnexal
torsion, and haemoperitoneum
doses:
By subcutaneous injection, in conjunction
with follicle-stimulating hormone, according to response
